description: Pubs and restaurants in Dublin remain closed. unless they can provide outdoor meals.
title: Coronavirus: Drink-only bars reopen outside Dublin
title_page: Coronavirus: Drink-only bars reopen outside Dublin - BBC News
maintext: Last week public health officials revealed that the "R" - the rate at which one person goes on to affect another - had risen to between 1.3 and 1.7 both in Dublin and across the state.
